    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/ed9610e90b9c1f67df7fbde5097c450c.avif?t=1638550080\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从零开始的实用音乐创作指南</h2></h2><br>《音乐：边做边学》（<i>Music: Pause and Play</i>）是一个可以动手的音乐创作科普。它将把创作分为节奏、音阶、旋律、和弦、低音线等部分，详细展开讲解。你可以跟着指引，一步步写出音乐片段。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><br><strong>- 绘制出你的音符和鼓点</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/0c226cfca45dca517e2da6b8582f3e4d.poster.avif?t=1638550080\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/0c226cfca45dca517e2da6b8582f3e4d.webm?t=1638550080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/0c226cfca45dca517e2da6b8582f3e4d.mp4?t=1638550080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>- 完成各种形式的音乐谜题挑战</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/7de0d3b7aa6558b7c8e01d7d67ac0fc0.poster.avif?t=1638550080\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/7de0d3b7aa6558b7c8e01d7d67ac0fc0.webm?t=1638550080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/7de0d3b7aa6558b7c8e01d7d67ac0fc0.mp4?t=1638550080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>- 开始了解丰富而有趣的乐理</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724790/extras/7f6d5d